# 📊 Tableau Hands-On Activity: Introduction to Tableau

---

## 🎯 Learning Objectives

After completing this activity, participants should be able to:

- Open Tableau Public
- Connect to an Excel or CSV file
- Identify Dimensions and Measures
- Create basic visualizations using drag-and-drop
- Apply filters and interactivity
- Build a simple dashboard

---

